  <body>
    <section name="GTOPO30 datasource">
      <p>
      The gtopo30 module contains a datasource that can read the GTOPO30 format into
      a standard feature collection. Write support is needed.
      You can download the GTOPO30 DEM files and get more information about this file
      format at the GTOPO30 home site at <a href="http://edcdaac.usgs.gov/gtopo30/gtopo30.html">http://edcdaac.usgs.gov/gtopo30/gtopo30.html</a>
      </p>
      <p>
      The create the datasource you'll need an URL pointing to one of the files that
      compose the standard GTOPO30 DEM, either .dem, .hdr, .src, .sch or .stx.
      </p>
    </section>
